<div class="nbunit" id="6Apr1938"><font color="red">6 April 1938</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Helen Joyce): I had a long letter from David [Fleischman] chiefly about Russian literature and his work. He wants to be a jazz critic &hellip; I have not seen Beckett for some weeks </div>
